data.description: Well maintained and an excellent value on Manhattan's east side! Large open floor plan features spacious living and dining with a super-functional kitchen including island with great storage. Master suite with bath featuring a soaking tub and TONS of closet space. Two generous additional bedrooms and full bath. Expanded deck offers great space to enjoy the outdoors! Two car garage, ample storage throughout. Only a few more years of LOW specials. Conveniently located close to EMS and Rec Center with easy access to KSU, Tuttle Creek and shopping! Smartphone control for HVAC and garage door! Call Cam today 785-340-5386.
